7. 如何在显示排名榜时，让其排名序号自动加一？
    forloop.counter的功能
    teacher-detail.html
    {% for hot_teacher in hot_teachers %}
       <dl class="des">
       <span class="num fl">{{ forloop.counter }}</span>

